c4 E-Commerce Platform

Shopper is a person | description Browses products and places orders
Admin is a person | description Manages inventory and fulfills orders

Storefront is a system | description Customer-facing web store
  -Serves product pages to [HTTPS]-> Shopper
  -Processes charges via [HTTPS]-> Payments
  -Sends fulfillment requests to [HTTPS]-> Warehouse

Payments is a system | description Stripe payment processing
  -Sends receipts to [Email]-> Shopper

Warehouse is a system | description Inventory and shipping management
  ~Sends tracking updates to [Email]~> Shopper

Back Office is a system | description Admin dashboard for order and inventory management
  -Provides management UI to [HTTPS]-> Admin
  -Queries stock levels from [HTTPS]-> Warehouse
  -Syncs catalog data [JSON/HTTPS]-> Storefront
  Storefront -Syncs catalog data [JSON/HTTPS]-> Back Office
